descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains the preprocessed data of BirdCLEF'24. For each audio file of the training dataset, I crop the center 5 seconds and convert it to spectrogram via CuPy. 

- [BirdCLEF'24 | Speed up audio-to-spec. via CuPy ](https://www.kaggle.com/code/zijiangyang1116/birdclef-24-speed-up-audio-to-spec-via-cupy): The description of the preprocessing method
- [BirdCLEF'24 | Preprocessing via CuPy](https://www.kaggle.com/code/zijiangyang1116/birdclef-24-preprocessing-via-cupy): Example of dataset preprocessing
- [BirdCLEF'24 | EfficientNetB0 PyTorch [Train]](https://www.kaggle.com/code/zijiangyang1116/birdclef-24-efficientnetb0-pytorch-train): Application of this dataset
title: BirdCLEF'24 | Spectrograms via CuPy
subtitle: Speed up audio-to-spec. via CuPy
